{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4ef3cf49d","title":"山东大学右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c7a4d3604e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"7f59b6c7ba","name":"山东大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e3ba3fa3b8","type":"title","text":"山东大学右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"434697e5c4","type":"authors","text":"山东大学学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"2cf89b12fd","type":"subtitle","text":"新党八股“成绩是主要的，缺点是难免的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"ce5365b186","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣！新党八股，“成绩是主要的；缺点是难免的”。在校肃反总结大会前，我系党总支召开了三四年级党团员大会，吸收我系肃反总结的意见。书记同志对肃反问题发言：“成绩是主要的；缺点是难免的，这是发动群众的必然结果。”请问：这是根据什么“经典著作”发动群众必然要出这样大的偏差！?(支书请注意我系具体情况)当同志们发表意见后，辅导员竟大加训斥……，这样发展下去是走投降主义路线……。试问：是否要我们共唱新党八股：“成绩是主要的，缺点是难免呐。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"b9485a78cc","type":"paragraph","text":" 物三全体同学","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"13329914fb","type":"subtitle","text":"祖国有一个阴暗的地方：山大","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"f02720a684","type":"paragraph","text":"怒吼吧！人！你知道在我们祖国有这样一个阴暗的地方，那里朝雾弥漫着，笼罩着一切，在那里积极分子在给主观与官僚送着贿赂，在那里善良的人为苦难所折磨！在那里时时可以望到“高贵”但又寒冷的心！然而真理永不会窒息在宗派主义的臭气中，有多少正直的灵魂在蒙眬的晨曦中痛苦呻吟！在那里生活是多么沉闷与寂寞！在那里在笑声中往往会飞来“政治问题”！在那里人们为“人权”而悲哀！……朋友，这个地方就是我们的山大！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"626c75fbc8","type":"paragraph","text":" 海二的一丛毒草","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"b84724adaa","type":"subtitle","text":"你要往上爬……","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"a550bba48e","type":"paragraph","text":"你要往上爬，容易，先与政治人物结婚，然后汇报一番，再拿棍子横冲，准备留作助教，再青云直上。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"7a82240f5d","type":"paragraph","text":" 生物系一群学生","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"b522bfe912","type":"subtitle","text":"肃反的唯一方式","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"54658692fa","type":"paragraph","text":"恐吓、逼供、污蔑、体罚、打击、开除，是党委会的肃反唯一方式！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"775353ad3d","type":"paragraph","text":" 生物系一群同学","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"2a3d8f9b43","type":"subtitle","text":"大学生中搞肃反有无必要","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"7d3e9b271f","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反问题，有无必要性，我有一点怀疑，即在大学生中搞肃反有无必要。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"6be3c4d07f","type":"paragraph","text":" 孙敬猷","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"},{"id":"0884bb970c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月25日《新山大》。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d"}],"page":{"id":"5139308dee","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4ef3cf49d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}